{"tid":279283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個譚仔食法","createTime":"2017-06-11T07:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T04:09:12.000Z","uid":106006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8396038b93c92da7b843180cbd3b295f51724886","tid":279283,"uid":106006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"我會叫 炸醬酸菜 重酸小辣 加多杯凍奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/150734_5778e9c792d44f358d5985fe892b6108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F150734_5778e9c792d44f358d5985fe892b6108.jpg&h=09c5e17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再將酸菜搬晒過去炸醬到 再撈埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一啖米線有晒炸醬加酸菜 好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  各位巴絲可以試下 一試上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9969a628b6c501e85706d55b0d7dd7f7ea06847","tid":279283,"uid":87047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"唔想自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746eef3beb3e7c28f5cbde5e5ad74ea29ffe3d43","tid":279283,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"淨米 大白肉"},{"pid":"a82db5bb789945e48ae3216cf7c6852508bcdabc","tid":279283,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"不了，驚引爆"},{"pid":"b70a5e84410b6c14042974052e87217c27844808","tid":279283,"uid":96983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"特辣走米線"},{"pid":"385b7aa787b93d676612cd15f9c4a8d932bcf313","tid":279283,"uid":13719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"淨米加豬耳<img src=\"/assets/face